                            <comment id="17629691" author="gaborgsomogyi" created="Mon, 7 Nov 2022 08:55:21 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;All other Kafka tests are also unstable. While I was hanging around the mentioned test I&apos;ve found a relatively big test code mistake which introduces race. Let me check whether it helps in this case...&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17629695" author="mapohl" created="Mon, 7 Nov 2022 08:57:04 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Awesome, thanks for picking up on that one &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=gaborgsomogyi&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;gaborgsomogyi&quot;&gt;gaborgsomogyi&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17629708" author="gaborgsomogyi" created="Mon, 7 Nov 2022 09:19:54 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Well, not saying I&apos;m able to fix this issue but I&apos;ve found a fundamental issue which is definitely a blocker in this area &lt;img class=&quot;emoticon&quot; src=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/images/icons/emoticons/smile.png&quot; height=&quot;16&quot; width=&quot;16&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; border=&quot;0&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17629711" author="gaborgsomogyi" created="Mon, 7 Nov 2022 09:28:03 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I&apos;ve added a PR, let&apos;s see the result. The test failures are super annoying and would be good to reach a better stability.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17637649" author="gaborgsomogyi" created="Wed, 23 Nov 2022 09:01:48 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Can we close this jira or the issue popped up again?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17638251" author="gaborgsomogyi" created="Thu, 24 Nov 2022 11:09:57 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;master: 9b6bae4eb87e1f472fd0f6cf9403911a88ed89ce&lt;br/&gt;
